text: Fräulein is the German language honorific previously in common use for unmarried women, comparable to Miss in English. Fräulein may also refer to: *"Fraulein" (song), a 1957 song *Fräulein (1958 film), a World War II film starring Dana Wynter and Mel Ferrer *Das Fräulein, a 2006 film ==See also== * *
title: Fräulein (disambiguation)
